* End-User: Residential Users, Office Workers, Students and Educators, Healthcare Patients and Staff, Industrial Workers
* Features: Adaptive Lighting, Programmable Schedules, Color Temperature Adjustment, Energy Monitoring Features, Remote Control Capabilities

